relation: Darrow5 - #01 A crushing blow releases all of Ness' built up PSI energy, which bursts forth as his strongest SMAAAASH!! attack yet bashes the rat into oblivion.
Darrow5 - #02 Smashing through the ceiling, the Plague Rat heads off to parts unknown. Also, he is permanently on fire.

Darrow5 - #03 Enrich Flavor has had a hard past couple of weeks. Thanks to Monotoli's recovery, things are looking up! Unfortunately, looking up may not be the healthiest thing for Enrich Flavor's sanity...
Darrow5 - #04 Coming back up to the surface, the group reaches Magnet Hill. Ness listens closely for the melody, which...is recorded somehow. Sound Stones! How do they work?

Darrow5 - #05 Although the people from Dalaam are highly regarded, sometimes they take the "being different" thing a little too far. Oh, sure, keys are great. But what about CARROT keys? Yeah, hey, that's normal, Dalaam. Whatever.
